# Cloudflare Pages redirect rules.
# No catch-all rule here — this intentionally disables SPA mode so that
# unmatched paths return a real 404 (served via 404.html) instead of 200.
#
# www → non-www redirects are handled by Cloudflare Redirect Rules (dashboard),
# not here. Pages _redirects absolute URL matching does not fire for custom
# domains registered on the same Pages project.
